ecause it was a beautiful garden, you know. They said it was one of the longest on Queens Park, those gardens in thirty-nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Where did your mother cook?
