Oh my word - my brother he used to have the chickens and he used to mark the eggs and blow the eggs and - have them all specimens you know, oh yes, I - I can always remember my eldest brother, you know, used to be cleaning the he
n-house out and you know, regimenting them up to bed of a night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 And you ate the eggs?
