\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 And sit in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes. Yes.
