Yes, that's right - as a family. Used to make our own music - that's what I said, we used to enjoy ourselves in, you know, very different way to what they enjoy themselves today. Their enjoyment is not our enjoyment you know - it wouldn't be our enjoyme
nt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did your parents play games with you at all?
