re was boot mending and all sorts of things to be done when they had spare time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Were there books in the house?
