\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 No, t
hey didn't have much time for that. She was always sewing - always - as I remember - her - machining or sewing - yes, machining - machining or sewing, yes. She was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1317777\charrsid9327351 machining}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
