I mean there was no time to sit there and look at television or anything like that, you know, there - there was something doing all the time in the home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Do you ever remember them reading aloud to each other?
