orn, you know, with all poppies and - corn swaying, you know, it was lovely. Yes, I did used to love that. And then of course we used to go out in a little trap, you know, they had a little trap and - my granddad used to drive at the back, you know, and w
e used to sit up the side in the front. We used to enjoy that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 It would be so different than here wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes, yes. It was only like a roundy sort of trap, you know, and got up two steps you know, to get in but we used to love to do that, yo
u know, to jump up in this trap.
