used to have to clean that out, you know, and tidy it up and do the floor and that and then we would have all the silver to clean and - we were kept busy I can tell you. We didn't have any - you know - Saturday we very seldom went to play like, you know, 
on a Saturday. We had work and jobs to do on a Saturday. And - during the week, you know, of course, as I say, I was able to go and play, you know, tennis or anything like that.
