\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes, yes, y
es. Oh, we had to keep our best clothes for our best clothes - and - and - yes - then we had to cover them up like we did the book and, you know, put them away for the next Sunday. But, I mean, you mustn't leave things about like they do today - throw all
 over the place, you know, you had to put them up tidily onto the pegs and things.
