 mean - although - my husband, he always went to church with me, you know, but I don't think they had the time then because they had such a big family, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Your father didn't go?
