llow and he was throwing this ball up and all of sudden it hit me in the ear and he never forgot to keep coming and asking me did it hurt me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 As an excuse?
