\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 No. No. No. The only thing I can remember is - when they used to have
 a penny affair, you know, used to go up in the - see that sometimes but there was nothing much then - not in those days - not like those now.
