Either my father or my mother, you know, it all depends. My eldest brother later on, he used to lash out on me - you know, give me for doing things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 What did you spend your pocket money on?
