't think that we was very extravagant in any of it really, I mean, you didn't have to be in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did you buy sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Just a few, yes, but not all that amount - I have more sweets now than ever I did in those days I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did it cost you money to play tennis?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Oh yes, you had to pay certain hours.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Would you used your pocket money for this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes, yes, yes, you had to use that, whatever you had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did anyone outside the home help your mother look after her house or family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 No. No. Only when - as I say, when the older ones grew up and of course they did their bit towards the home. No, no.
