\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Well, they'd come to see them I suppose, you know, they used to come and see them. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
