\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes. Yes, he had his own. Mr Childers and
 he lives in - Loffdrop Street, well least his dead now, Mrs Jones is still there - she's ninety something. Now, Mr Childers used to take me round the police stations when I was a little one and show me to all the policemen because I was such a bonny baby
. Yes, that's Mr Childers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Would your father go out with him?
