Well I knew him when I was about fourteen or fifteen I think but we first went out for outing together on the church you know and we used to go to Ruislip and Rickmansworth and all sorts of places and have our tea and our, you know, used to cycle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 So you knew him about six or seven years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes.
