\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did you ever make your own medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did you bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Oh, yes, yes I have bottle fruit before. I've broke some bottles too. Pouring it on and putting it in the oven too hot.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did you manage to grow any vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Yes, we 
