he cricket, you know, we'd sit there for a day and used to thoroughly enjoy it, you know. And of course as I say you both want to be interested in that sort of thing to enjoy a thing. You see, I like sport and I - I used to love cricket. Yes, and I love t
he open air, you know. Don't get so much of it now, but still, I've had me chances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did you ever go away for a holiday?
