o a football match or something like that, you know, when it was nice out to Chelsea, you know. And, that used to be a nice outing, you know, to go to Chelsea, that's quite a good way to go, you know, from where we were and that would give us a little bit
 of pleasure. But that wasn't always pretty often, you know, now and again. And on Sundays we used to go to St Judes Church which is not there at the moment - that got taken down - that was the end of that.
