\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Did you belong to any sick clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1008777 GB  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7014491 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid10888220\charrsid9327351 Or funeral clubs or anything like that?
